title: Cupertino Condo  – Two Bedroom Suites / Penthouse
posting_body: ['This large (1800 sq. ft.)', '2/2 townhouse at Cupertino/Los Altos/Sunnyvale right at 280/Foothill.', 'Quiet secure complex.', ' Walk to Trader Joes, Lucky, Starbucks, Wells Fargo, Woodland Library and more.', 'Walk to school at West Valley Elementary, Cupertino Middle or Homestead.', '  No Common walls / Top floor – 18 foot vaulted ceilings, bright and light.', ' Separate eat in kitchen, open concept dining room / living, built in buffet area.', '  Bedrooms have 9’ ceilings and 2 closets each – both bathrooms have double vanity and separate WC.', '  4 parking spaces in underground gated parking lot.', '  Private balcony with 2 large storage closets.', ' Pool, hot tub and Clubhouse   Full sized Washer/Dryer included.', '  1 year lease with option to extend.', ' No Smoking, and excellent credit required.', ' Water included.', 'Available ASAP', '$3900/month - $ 4500 deposit.']
